Classic Cat Food is 100% nutritionally balanced and complete natural cat food, suitable from kittens to older cats. Made in the UK with natural ingredients, we draw upon three generations of British farming heritage and pet care expertise to ensure your cat enjoys a healthy and hearty meal.

Purina Friskies boasts over 100 different cat food options of yummy wet and dry foods, treats, and cat food complements. Friskies cat food is carefully formulated with a blend of nutritious ingredients to cater to every cat breed\'s diet needs and support overall pet health.
Applaws Natural Cat Food is carefully made with premium ingredients to ensure your pet is as healthy and happy as they can be.

If you own a cat, you may wonder what the best dry cat food is so you can make sure she’s getting the nutrition she needs. Our natural, highly digestible formulas* have real meat as the #1 ingredient and added vitamins, minerals and nutrients to help support your cat’s whole body health.
